data.description: Renovated 3-Bed Home Near Century High School - Great opportunity, Great price for first home buyers and investors at 6399 SE Johnson St! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven, recently renovated in 2020, The transformative update brought a third bedroom, a full bathroom, and upgrades a new roof, vinyl siding, windows, and a water heater. A winning combination of style and functionality. Step inside to experience spacious and comfortable living, striking the perfect balance between privacy and togetherness. The fully-fenced backyard is your private oasis, ideal for relaxation or entertaining, while the tandem driveway provides hassle-free off-street parking. And guess what? NO HOA to worry about! Centrally located near Century High School, Francis Park, and the vibrant South Hillsboro district, this property grants easy access to schools, green spaces, and a variety of restaurants, shops, and amenities. The potential for an ADU (Accessory Dwelling Unit) introduces an exciting opportunity for extra income or extended family living. This property offers modern updates and endless possibilities, making it an exceptional choice for those looking to establish roots or make investment. The clock is ticking! Schedule a viewing today and unlock the potential of 6399 SE Johnson St at an irresistible price! . Great opportunity !! Don't Miss
